---
import Container from "./Container.astro"

---

<div id="features" class="bg-black py-32">
  <Container>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-4 bg-orange-50 flex flex-col items-center p-8 relative isolate">
        <div class="absolute w-1/2 h-full min-h-full min-w-[50%] top-0 left-0 bottom-0 bg-orange-100 z-0"></div>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left text-5xl text-orange-500 mt-8 z-[1]"></i>
        <p class="text-center text-2xl font-thin text-neutral-700 my-4 z-[1]">Design is everything, and these guys have nailed it.</p>
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 z-[1]">Company</p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 flex flex-col items-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-light text-white">No Hassle, just quality!</h2>
        <p class="text-white text-xl font-thin mt-8 mb-16">Professional Video Editing Services meant for Entrepreneusr,, businessmne, creators!</p>
        <div class="w-full grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-8">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-film text-white text-5xl"></i>
            <p class="text-white w-2/3 text-center font-light">As many videos you like for a fixed price!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-8">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-clock text-white text-5xl"></i>
            <p class="text-white w-2/3 text-center font-light">Get videos blazingly fast within few business days!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-8">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-hand-holding-heart text-white text-5xl"></i>
            <p class="text-white w-2/3 text-center font-light">We'll revise the designs until you're 100% satisfied.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-48">
      <div>

      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-white font-light text-3xl text-center">
          Editing Agency for Socials by a YouTuber!<br /><br /><br />
          Hi, I am pixelk Samy I am a youtuber myself!<br /><br />
          While teaching people on Youtube for over half a decade! I finally decided to help out everyone around the whole who wants to take their videos to the nect level!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>